    <briefdescription>
<para>Abstract base class for layout managers. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1Layout" kindref="compound">Layout</ref> managers are responsible for measuring and arranging child views within a container. They implement the specific layout algorithms for different layout types (stack, grid, flex, etc.).</para>
<para><ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1LayoutManager" kindref="compound">LayoutManager</ref> works with <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1ViewImpl" kindref="compound">ViewImpl</ref> for direct access to implementation details during layout calculations. This allows any <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1View" kindref="compound">View</ref> (or derived class) to have layout capability.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>This is an internal class. It is not intended to be used directly by applications. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
